336
00:19:22,050 --> 00:19:23,650
Did you read it properly, kid?

337
00:19:23,850 --> 00:19:25,150
You probably don't know.

338
00:19:25,950 --> 00:19:32,150
Because otherwise you'd see that clause 17B... I'm saying...

339
