369
00:21:32,570 --> 00:21:35,910
Marek Vasut, president of the Studs.

370
00:21:35,910 --> 00:21:37,990
Ozzak, metal god.

371
00:21:51,650 --> 00:21:53,840
So daddy was being sensitive.

372
